 Boris Milat detailed how his brother , Ivan , shot and paralysed a taxi driver in 1962 , more then 25 years before he went on a backpacker killing spree .
Neville Knight was shot on March 6 , 1962 , by a 17-year-old Milat who was riding in the back of his taxi .
Alan Dillon was convicted for the shooting and spent five years behind bars .